cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.RO, cs.GR 

This paper deals with the task of estimating the topology of road networks from aerial images using a Convolutional Neural Network (CNN). Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves deep learning techniques, which makes cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) another likely category. The use of CNNs also suggests that cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a possible category. The paper also involves robotics and automation, which makes cs.RO (Robotics and Automation) another likely category. Finally, the paper deals with the extraction of complex networks, which makes cs.GR (Graphics) a possible category.
